## Monetization Models

### 1. Internal Platform (Recommended)

The system can be deployed internally as an **AI capability platform**.

#### Value:

* Reduces manual analysis time
* Improves productivity
* Enhances decision-making

#### Monetization:

* Cost savings
* Efficiency gains

---

### 2. Service / API Model

The system can be exposed as a service:

Example:

```
POST /analyze-stock
```

Other teams or applications can consume it.

#### Monetization:

* Pay-per-use
* Internal chargeback model
* Service-based integration

---

### 3. SaaS Model (Future Scope)

The system can evolve into a product:

* Web dashboard
* User login
* Analytics interface

#### Monetization:

* Subscription-based (monthly/yearly)
* Tiered access plans

---

## Role of LLM Training

### Important Clarification

This solution does NOT rely on custom LLM training.

Instead, it uses:

* Pre-trained models (Phi-3, Mistral)
* Context injection via RAG
* Structured prompting
* Tool-based augmentation

### Key Insight

The value lies in **how the model is used**, not in training the model itself.

